Data protection information
Status: 01.08.2024
So that you can understand the processing of your data in connection with your use of the
Ambit-OurSports app (hereinafter "Ambit app"), we would like to provide you with an
overview of this processing. The following data protection information contains general
information about how we handle your data and information about your rights under the
European General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and the German Federal Data
Protection Act (BDSG).

